                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#11v" facs="013">Fol. 11v</locus>
                    folio has been washed, likely in preparation for painting
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <desc>
                      words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#26v #27r #36r #37r #37v #40v" facs="028 037 038 039 042">folss. 26v, 27r, 36r, 37r, 37v, 40v, </locus>);
